    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
      <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Aink418-kilavi">ituvum atu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">And this is that.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <lg xml:id="Aink418">        
            <l>vāṉam pāṭi vaṟaṅkaḷain tāṉā</l>
            <l>taḻituḷi talaiiya puṟaviṟ kāṇvara</l>
            <l>vāṉara makaḷō nīyē</l>
            <l>māṇmulai yaṭaiya muyaṅki yōyē.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the woodland where unending destructive rains poured down,</l> 
<l>removing the drought of the skylarks, have you </l>
<l>who embraced me so that [your] glorious breast grew close,</l> 
<l>come to be seen as a celestial woman of the heavens?</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </body>
